com.impinj.octane

Class TagFilter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.impinj.octane.TagFilter

  • public class TagFilter
extends java.lang.Object
    A class to hold the configuration of a tag inventory filter. Tag inventory filters are applied during the reader inventory operation. These inventory filters are built from gen2 select commands.
    See Also:
    Gen2 Standard page 58
